<template><div><h1 id="markdown-input" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#markdown-input"><span>Markdown input</span></a></h1>
<p>A markdown editor control for <code v-pre>JsonForm</code>. Use <code v-pre>ControlBuilder.properties('field').markdown()</code> to render a rich-text markdown editor instead of a plain text input.</p>
